&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;In this role you will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Lead the design and evolution of distributed systems that power our OT/IoT cybersecurity platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Drive architecture decisions with a long-term perspective on scalability, performance, and maintainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Own cross-team initiatives, aligning engineering efforts with product and business priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Identify and systematically reduce technical debt, improving system reliability and developer productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Act as a technical multiplier, mentoring engineers and raising the bar on design, code quality, and operational&amp;nbsp;excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Define and champion best practices in software design, testing, and observability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Collaborate closely with Product, SRE, and Security teams to deliver end-to-end solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Influence and improve engineering processes, ensuring effective delivery in a fast-paced agile environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Take ownership of mission-critical features and services, from concept through production and beyond&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Embody Nozomi Networks’ cultural pillars, promoting transparency, trust, and accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
